《'''唐朝小栗子'''》是[[大愛電視|大愛電視]]的動畫節目，开播于2007年4月7日。该作品最初开播时是2D动画，自2011年2月以后转变为[[3D动画|3D动画]]。

2014年，获得最佳3D動畫獎。<ref>{{cite news|language =zh-tw|url =http://star.ettoday.net/news/426078|title =過去跑船、賣玩偶　班鐵翔入行30多年終問鼎亞太影帝  娛樂星光雲|publisher =ETtoday東森新聞雲|accessdate =2017-01-01|archive-date =2016-11-30|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20161130112519/http://star.ettoday.net/news/426078|dead-url =no}}</ref>而大愛電視台和韓國公共教育電視台簽訂合約結為姊妹台，<ref>{{cite news|language =zh-tw|url =http://star.ettoday.net/news/430579|title =有一樣的理念！　大愛臺與韓國EBS簽約交換節目|publisher =ETtoday東森新聞雲|accessdate =2017-01-01|archive-date =2022-03-31|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20220331045052/https://star.ettoday.net/news/430579|dead-url =no}}</ref>也获得电视金钟奖动画节目奖。<ref>{{cite news |title=49届金钟奖提名揭晓 蓝正龙天心有望当视帝视后- 中国日报网 |url=http://covid-19.chinadaily.com.cn/hqcj/xfly/2014-09-18/content_12407161.html |accessdate=2021-10-09 |work=中国日报 |archive-date=2021-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211022231134/http://covid-19.chinadaily.com.cn/hqcj/xfly/2014-09-18/content_12407161.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=大愛兒少節目 金鐘入圍7項放異彩 |url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/news/%E5%A4%A7%E6%84%9B%E5%85%92%E5%B0%91%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-%E9%87%91%E9%90%98%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%8D7%E9%A0%85%E6%94%BE%E7%95%B0%E5%BD%A9-044536607.html |accessdate=2021-10-09 |work=雅虎新聞 |language=zh-TW |archive-date=2021-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211031212515/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/news/%E5%A4%A7%E6%84%9B%E5%85%92%E5%B0%91%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-%E9%87%91%E9%90%98%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%8D7%E9%A0%85%E6%94%BE%E7%95%B0%E5%BD%A9-044536607.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>内容鼓励小朋友通过努力克服困难。<ref>{{cite news|language =zh-tw|url =http://company.xinmin.cn/latest/2011/08/11/11691602.html|title =住院生活不枯燥 患儿在远大感受温情_最新|publisher =新民网|deadurl =yes|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140827172450/http://company.xinmin.cn/latest/2011/08/11/11691602.html|archivedate =2014-08-27|accessdate =2017-01-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=第49屆金鐘獎完整入圍名單 雨後驕陽10項最大贏家 |url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/402824 |accessdate=2021-10-09 |work=ETto